NAME
    WWW::Scraper::WolframAlpha - Scrape WolframAlpha
    <http://www.wolframalpha.com> and return a result

SYNOPSIS
        my $wa = WWW::Scraper::WolframAlpha->new;

        say $wa->reply("10 usd to eur");

DESCRIPTION
    A simple scraper for WolframAlpha for people too lazy to sign up for the
    API.

